value.string: Second floor location 1 Bedroom/1 Bathroom Time Interval unit located in The Whaler Tower I. Relax on beautiful Kaanapali Beach during the early fall. The Whaler on Kaanapali Beach offers amenities that include an ocean view pool along the famed Kaanapali Beach walk, spa, sauna, workout gym, salon, underground parking, and a business hub center. Take a walk in the center courtyard while enjoying the tropical landscaping and Koi fish pond.
